  "page": "Hook",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Kings_landing_map.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/4/46/Kings_landing_map.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Kings_landing_map.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>1 <a href=\"/index.php/Rosby_road\" title=\"Rosby road\">Rosby road</a>, 2 <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_Gate\" title=\"Dragon Gate\">Dragon Gate</a>, 3 <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Gate\" title=\"Iron Gate\">Iron Gate</a>, 4 <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonpit\" title=\"Dragonpit\">Dragonpit</a>, 5 <a href=\"/index.php/Shae%27s_manse\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shae&#39;s manse\">Shae's manse</a>, 6 <a href=\"/index.php/Chataya%27s_brothel\" title=\"Chataya&#39;s brothel\">Chataya's brothel</a>, 7 <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Gate\" title=\"Old Gate\">Old Gate</a>, 8 <a href=\"/index.php/Flea_Bottom\" title=\"Flea Bottom\">Flea Bottom</a>, 9 <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>, 10 <a href=\"/index.php/Street_of_the_Sisters\" title=\"Street of the Sisters\">Street of the Sisters</a>, 11 <a href=\"/index.php/Gate_of_the_Gods\" title=\"Gate of the Gods\">Gate of the Gods</a>, 12 <a href=\"/index.php/Cobbler%27s_Square\" title=\"Cobbler&#39;s Square\">Cobbler's Square</a>, 13 <a href=\"/index.php/Guildhall_of_the_Alchemists\" title=\"Guildhall of the Alchemists\">Guildhall of the Alchemists</a>, <b>14 Hook</b>, 15 <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Sept_of_Baelor\" title=\"Great Sept of Baelor\">Great Sept of Baelor</a>, 16 <a href=\"/index.php/Muddy_Way\" title=\"Muddy Way\">Muddy Way</a>, 17 <a href=\"/index.php/Fishmonger%27s_Square\" title=\"Fishmonger&#39;s Square\">Fishmonger's Square</a>, 18 <a href=\"/index.php/River_Gate\" title=\"River Gate\">River Gate</a>, 19 <a href=\"/index.php/Shop_of_Tobho_Mott\" title=\"Shop of Tobho Mott\">Tobho Mott's shop</a>, 20 <a href=\"/index.php/Street_of_Steel\" title=\"Street of Steel\">Street of Steel</a>, 21 <a href=\"/index.php/Harbor_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Harbor of King&#39;s Landing\">harbor</a>, 22 <a href=\"/index.php/Lion_Gate\" title=\"Lion Gate\">Lion Gate</a>, 23 <a href=\"/index.php/River_Row\" title=\"River Row\">River Row</a>, 24 <a href=\"/index.php/Fish_market\" title=\"Fish market\">fish market</a>, 25 <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_grounds_(King%27s_Landing)\" title=\"Tourney grounds (King&#39;s Landing)\">tourney grounds</a>, 26 <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Gate\" title=\"King&#39;s Gate\">King's Gate</a>, 27 <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">kingsroad</a></div></div></div>\n<p>The <b> Hook</b> is a narrow, curved street<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> which begins at the <a href=\"/index.php/Muddy_Way\" title=\"Muddy Way\">Muddy Way</a> near <a href=\"/index.php/Fishmonger%27s_Square\" title=\"Fishmonger&#39;s Square\">Fishmonger's Square</a> and climbs part of <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_High_Hill\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s High Hill\">Aegon's High Hill</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafking.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafking.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> It connects with another prominent street (presumably the <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Way\" title=\"King&#39;s Way\">King's Way</a>) which continues on to the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> atop the hill.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hook&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Riot_of_King%27s_Landing_(Dance_of_the_Dragons)\" title=\"Riot of King&#39;s Landing (Dance of the Dragons)\">Violent riots</a> occurred in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen_Manderly\" title=\"Torrhen Manderly\">Torrhen Manderly</a> led a sortie from the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> down the Hook with his <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a> to try to stop the rioters. When they arrived at the <a href=\"/index.php/Fishmonger%27s_Square\" title=\"Fishmonger&#39;s Square\">Fishmonger's Square</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/River_Row\" title=\"River Row\">River Row</a>, the region was swarming with Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Perkin_the_Flea\" title=\"Perkin the Flea\">Perkin the Flea</a>'s gutter <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a>. Torrhen lost a quarter of his men fighting his way back to the Red Keep.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hook&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hook&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I Baratheon's</a> party returns to the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> after saying goodbye to Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Myrcella_Baratheon\" title=\"Myrcella Baratheon\">Myrcella Baratheon</a> at the docks. While they are riding up the Hook, a woman walks out of the crowd of <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> with a dead baby and blocks the way. <a href=\"/index.php/Riots_in_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Riots in King&#39;s Landing\">Riots in King's Landing</a> ensue after an altercation between the royal party and the crowd.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hook&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> passes by the Hook while traveling to meet <a href=\"/index.php/Symon_Silver_Tongue\" title=\"Symon Silver Tongue\">Symon Silver Tongue</a> at a <a href=\"/index.php/Winesink\" title=\"Winesink\">winesink</a> near <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya%27s_Hill\" title=\"Visenya&#39;s Hill\">Visenya's Hill</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hook&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_41\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 41\">Chapter 41</a>, Tyrion IX.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafking.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafking.27s_landing.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, King's Landing.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Map_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Map of King&#39;s Landing\">Map of King's Landing</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Overthrown.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_32\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 32\">Chapter 32</a>, Tyrion IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260407210212\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.024 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.025 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 441/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8746/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 2063/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 384/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2678/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   12.418      1 -total\n 74.62%    9.266      5 Template:Ref\n 43.94%    5.456      5 Template:Ref/core\n 20.45%    2.539      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26714-0!canonical and timestamp 20260407210220 and revision id 335718\n -->\n",
